 Today Before Tomorrow's \"Complete Demolition\" of Iran | The Gateway Pundit | by Jordan Conradson"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZHdPkkF", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 23, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8541673, "raw_content": "This literally happened to me at work during COVID. I was the only person who refused to get the COVID mRNA poison, and my boss mocked me and asked if I was a \"conspiracy theorist\" that believed the Earth was flat too.\n\nIn my view, the Deep State is now using bots across social media to make it look like MAGA or anyone who's sceptical believes crazy shit, so that they have less credibility when something real DOES come up in the future.\n\nThoughts? All the \"Artemis is fake!\" comments on this site and Reddit look like they're from bot accounts.", "author": "HeCantDoIt", "created": 1775562564073, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "PatriotBh", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Opinion: The Deep State is astroturfing sentiment that \"the Artemis mission is fake!\" to hurt people who ask questions. Just like how when you questioned the Poison COVID Vax, you got made fun of for believing the Earth was flat too.", "last_comment_created": 1775564817332, "content": "<p>This literally happened to me at work during COVID. I was the only person who refused to get the COVID mRNA poison, and my boss mocked me and asked if I was a &quot;conspiracy theorist&quot; that believed the Earth was flat too.</p>\n<p>In my view, the Deep State is now using bots across social media to make it look like MAGA 